```css
.yellow-highlight {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  z-index: 1;
}

.yellow-highlight::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 5px;
  left: -2%;
  width: 104%;
  height: 35%;
  background-color: var(--yellow);
  z-index: -1;
  transform: rotate(-1deg);
}
```

